9, 2016
Product received for free
												This game is extreme fun to play. The idea behind this game is unique and inovative. We played a few rounds and randomly ended up in a lobby with a dev. They have so much ideas and in the test build you can already see what might end up in the game.One thing to notice is, that the community is very small at the moment. So bring your friends or ask in the forums for people to join you (;
